ia","Hebrew_Bible","Annals","Shalmaneser_III","Adad-Nirari_III","Tiglath-Pileser_III","Stele","Tel_Dan_Stele","Eritrea","Samos_Island","Zakkur_stele","Israel","David","Tiglath-Pileser_I","Hazael","Unqi","Israel","Golan_Heights","Sea_of_Galilee","Rezin","Tiglath-Pileser_III","Assyria","732_BCE","Pekah","Kingdom_of_Israel_(Samaria)","Ahaz","King_of_Judah","Iron_Age","Tell-Ashtara","Tell_er-Rumeith","Et-Tell","Tel-Dan","Tell_el-Oreme","Hadadezer","Hazael","Ben-Hadad_III","Rezin","Aram_(Biblical_region)","Aram_Naharaim","Aram_Rehob"]}